strings: <voice_0x01000BFF><se_low>King Trode: Medea! My Medea! You're safe!

<voice_0x01000C00><se_low>King Trode: Were you lonely without me?
There, there! It's all right!
We'll leave this horrible place at once.

<voice_0x01000C01><se_low>King Trode: The Princess and I will go on ahead.
Make sure you're not too far behind!

<voice_0x01000C04><se_def>Angelo: You'd have to work pretty hard to mess up
your escape from here. Anyway, I'm sorry for
all the trouble.

<voice_0x01000C05><se_def>Angelo: So this is farewell.
May the Goddess watch over you on your journey.
